  "None suggested yet": "Ingen forslag ennå",
  "After the AI responds, a separate quiet API call generates the tracker JSON independently. Expect ~250–300s total per message (narrative + wait + tracker).": "Etter svaret genererer et stille kall JSON. ~250–300s/melding.",
  "✓ Single API call — typically ~100–120s total": "✓ Ett API-kall — ~100–120s",
  "✓ No profile switching — eliminates message deletion risk": "✓ Ingen profilbytte — ingen risiko",
  "✓ AI has full narrative context for accurate tracking": "✓ AI har full kontekst",
  "✓ 2–3× faster than Separate mode in practice": "✓ 2–3× raskere enn Separat",
  "✗ Uses tokens from the main response budget (~1,700 tokens for tracker)": "✗ Bruker tokens fra hovedbudsjettet (~1 700)",
