  "✗ Two API calls per message — 2–3× slower than Together mode": "✗ To API-kall — 2–3× tregere",
  "✗ ~12s dead time between calls (chat save + preset switching)": "✗ ~12s dødtid mellom kall",
  "✗ Tracker prompt is ~10K+ tokens at 8 context msgs — reduce to 3–4 for speed": "✗ Prompt ~10K+ ved 8 meldinger — reduser til 3–4",
  "✗ Profile switching can cause message deletion (race condition with other extensions)": "✗ Profilbytte kan slette meldinger",
  "✗ Embeds previous snapshot into narrative call (~1.9K tokens) unless Embed snapshots = 0": "✗ Bygger inn snapshot (~1.9K) med mindre = 0",
  "How many recent messages to include when generating tracker updates.": "Hvor mange nylige meldinger.",
  "Separate mode only — Together mode uses ST's full context automatically.": "Kun Separat — Sammen bruker STs kontekst.",
  "Fastest. Good for simple 1-on-1 scenes (~5K token prompt)": "Raskeste. For 1-mot-1-scener (~5K)",
  "Balanced. Recommended for most scenes (~8–12K tokens)": "Balansert. For de fleste (~8–12K)",
  "Better continuity for complex multi-character scenes (~12–20K tokens)": "Bedre kontinuitet for komplekse scener (~12–20K)",
  "Maximum context but significantly slower and more expensive": "Maksimal kontekst men tregere og dyrere",
  "This is the biggest factor in Separate mode speed. At 8 msgs your tracker prompt is ~10K tokens — doubling roughly doubles generation time. Lower values (3–4) can cut tracker time by 40–60%.": "Største faktor. 8 meldinger ~10K — dobling dobler. 3–4 reduserer 40–60%.",
  "Separate mode only.": "Kun Separat modus.",
  "How many times to retry if the tracker API call returns invalid JSON.": "Antall forsøk ved ugyldig JSON.",
  "Built-in preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Optimized for structured JSON output on GLM-5.": "Forhåndsinnstilling: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. For JSON på GLM-5.",
  "Embed recent scene snapshots into the narrative conversation context so the AI can reference tracker state while writing. Only applies in Separate mode. The tracker's own API call always receives the previous snapshot regardless of this setting.": "Bygger inn øyeblikksbilder. Kun Separat. Trackeren mottar alltid den forrige.",
  "Each embedded snapshot adds ~1.9K tokens to your narrative prompt. Set to 0 to eliminate this overhead — the tracker API call still receives previous state independently. Set to 1 for narrative continuity (AI remembers scene details). Values above 1 are rarely beneficial.": "Hvert snapshot +~1.9K. 0 fjerner. 1 for kontinuitet. Over 1 sjelden nyttig.",
  "Injected as invisible context — AI treats it as authoritative background info. Best for continuity without polluting the conversation.": "Injisert som usynlig kontekst — autoritativ bakgrunn.",
